                                    </span>
                                }
                                else
                                {

                                    <span> is in Progress.</span>
                                }

                            </h1>
                            <h1 style="font-size: 18px; color:#333; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">Below are the full details of your transaction:</h1>
